NAME

findmydevice-user-agent — Find My Mac user agent

SYNOPSIS

findmydevice-user-agent

DESCRIPTION

findmydevice-user-agent is the user agent for Find My Mac.

There are no configuration options to findmydevice-user-agent. Users should not run it manually.

1/11/14 Mac OS X
